name: Abraham Warjus
description: I am a man of many talents, and the guardian of my life.I have the strength of my God, to lead me through whatever Life has in store for me.I shall look ahead, rather than be pulled back to past sorrows or mistakes, for only by moving forward can I begin a new. I will pray for those I love, that my love may be their blessings, that my prayers will be their strength.I am a very down to earth man who’s searching for his missing part.
